All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Closeable
public class LzoJsonRecordReader
extends LzoRecordReader<org.apache.hadoop.io.LongWritable,org.apache.hadoop.io.MapWritable>

Reads line from an lzo compressed text file, and decodes each line into a json map. Skips lines that are invalid json. WARNING: Does not handle multi-line json input well, if at all. TODO: Fix that, and keep Hadoop counters for invalid vs. valid lines.
